52
00:02:12,007 --> 00:02:13,759
Got it.

53
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:14,968
Sure you don't want one?

54
00:02:15,010 --> 00:02:17,012
[MAKI]
No, thanks.

55
00:02:17,054 --> 00:02:18,639
[TENNIS GIRLS]
One!

56
