61
00:02:33,820 --> 00:02:37,074
but nobody really uses it,
so we kind of moved in.

62
00:02:37,115 --> 00:02:39,409
It works for us 'cause it's
right next to the tennis courts.

63
00:02:39,451 --> 00:02:42,079
[MAKI] So it's like you've got
a club room all to yourselves.

64
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:43,205
