67
00:02:52,214 --> 00:02:54,841
Oh! And they're so light, too.

68
00:02:54,883 --> 00:02:55,926
Can I really keep them?

69
00:02:55,967 --> 00:02:57,010
Sure.

70
00:02:57,052 --> 00:02:58,553
