So you might as well use it.

74
00:03:08,605 --> 00:03:10,399
Otherwise it'll just get tossed.

75
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:14,236
Ah. No point letting
it go to waste then.

76
00:03:14,277 --> 00:03:15,987
We're out of ball caps.

77
00:03:16,029 --> 00:03:17,989
[MAKI]
Hey, what's this?

78
00:03:18,031 --> 00:03:19,366
[TOMA]
Itsuki's sister gave it to him,

79
00:03:19,408 --> 00:03:21,326
but he didn't want it.

80
00:03:21,368 --> 00:03:23,954
Finders keepers. Let's see.

81
00:03:25,372 --> 00:03:26,164
Like it?

82
00:03:26,206 --> 00:03:27,332
It fits fine.

83
00:03:27,374 --> 00:03:29,835
It's just usually only
the girls wear sun visors.

84
00:03:29,876 --> 00:03:34,089
Who cares? I think
it looks cool. He, he!

85
00:03:34,131 --> 00:03:36,967
For real, Katsuragi?
What're you thinking?

86
00:03:37,008 --> 00:03:40,846
Why would you wanna be
in a garbage club like that?

87
00:03:40,887 --> 00:03:41,722
[KENDO GIRL 2A]
We're late!

88
00:03:41,763 --> 00:03:43,306
[KENDO GIRL 2B]
C'mon, hurry!

89
00:03:49,688 --> 00:03:50,939
Uh?

90
00:03:56,611 --> 00:03:57,863
Hey, there they are.

91
00:03:57,904 --> 00:03:59,281
Uh‐‐

92
00:04:00,657 --> 00:04:02,033
You guys!

93
00:04:04,453 --> 00:04:06,788
Wow, how did he
already get a uniform?

94
00:04:06,830 --> 00:04:08,749
Hah. You get that
visor from the girls?

95
00:04:08,790 --> 00:04:11,585
[BOYS chuckle]

96
00:04:11,626 --> 00:04:13,837
Welcome to the Soft Tennis Club.

97
00:04:13,879 --> 00:04:16,006
I'm Rintaro Futsu,
the vice president.

98
00:04:16,047 --> 00:04:19,092
Class 2‐D. Nice to meet you.

99
00:04:19,134 --> 00:04:22,846
Uh. So, uh. How about
you introduce yourself

100
00:04:22,888 --> 00:04:25,599
to the rest of the team?

101
00:04:25,640 --> 00:04:30,270
Okay. Maki Katsuragi
from Class 2‐C.

102
00:04:31,897 --> 00:04:32,856
That's it.

103
00:04:32,898 --> 00:04:34,191
Okay...?

104
00:04:34,232 --> 00:04:35,192
Funny guy, huh?

105
00:04:35,233 --> 00:04:37,694
Easy, Tsubasa, try not
to scare off the new guy.

106
00:04:37,736 --> 00:04:40,071
Seriously, if he quits,
it'll totally kill

107
00:04:40,113 --> 00:04:41,448
the captain's enthusiasm‐‐

108
00:04:41,490 --> 00:04:42,657
Hey, what's this?

109
00:04:42,699 --> 00:04:44,910
Feeling brave enough
to talk back, Taiyo, huh?

110
00:04:44,951 --> 00:04:46,328
[TAIYO]
Ow, ow, ow, stop it!

111
00:04:46,369 --> 00:04:47,829
That's enough, Tsubasa.

112
00:04:47,871 --> 00:04:50,165
Stop messing with Taiyo.

113
00:04:50,207 --> 00:04:53,126
I'm Shingo Takenouchi,
from Class 2‐A.

114
00:04:53,168 --> 00:04:57,088
Anyone ever tell you that
you're kinda short? Huh?

115
00:04:57,130 --> 00:05:00,091
[ITSUKI]
I'm Itsuki Ameno. Class 2‐B.

116
00:05:00,133 --> 00:05:01,718
And I honestly have no idea why

117
00:05:01,760 --> 00:05:03,345
you'd wanna be
in this crappy club.

118
00:05:03,386 --> 00:05:05,764
Tsubasa Soga from Class 2‐B.

119
00:05:05,806 --> 00:05:07,349
Don't make me hit you.

120
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:09,976
Uh... He's just joking around!

121
00:05:10,018 --> 00:05:11,645
He's not gonna hit you.

122
00:05:11,686 --> 00:05:15,357
My name's Nao Tsukinose,
from Class 2‐A.

123
00:05:15,398 --> 00:05:17,150
Hey, you wanna hear
something cool?

124
00:05:17,192 --> 00:05:18,777
Did you know
Nishikori is actually

125
00:05:18,819 --> 00:05:21,279
my mom's cousin, seriously!

126
00:05:21,321 --> 00:05:23,114
For real? Ow!

127
00:05:23,156 --> 00:05:24,783
No, it's not for real.

128
00:05:24,825 --> 00:05:25,784
You should know better.

129
00:05:25,826 --> 00:05:27,452
Yeah, good point.

130
00:05:27,494 --> 00:05:29,329
Nao is always making up stories.

131
00:05:29,371 --> 00:05:32,666
Oh! I didn't go yet, did I?

132
00:05:32,707 --> 00:05:35,210
Taiyo Ishigami, Class 2‐A.

133
00:05:35,252 --> 00:05:38,088
Yeah, my parents decided
to name me after the sun.

134
00:05:38,129 --> 00:05:41,091
So I try to be as warm
to people as I can.

135
00:05:41,132 --> 00:05:44,010
[TOMA] Now you know all
seven of our club members.

136
00:05:44,052 --> 00:05:46,513
And Katsuragi makes eight.

137
00:05:46,555 --> 00:05:48,723
You and me are going to pair up.

138
00:05:48,765 --> 00:05:51,101
Wait. I thought I would
be playing alone.

139
00:05:51,142 --> 00:05:54,062
Sorry, but everybody in
our club plays doubles.

140
00:05:54,104 --> 00:05:55,897
And most middle school
soft tennis clubs

141
00:05:55,939 --> 00:05:58,191
actually don't do
any singles games.

142
00:05:58,233 --> 00:05:59,943
All right, let's hit the courts.

143
00:05:59,985 --> 00:06:01,653
I'll teach you the
basics of soft tennis.

144
00:06:01,695 --> 00:06:03,738
Hey. Hold on a minute, Captain.

145
00:06:03,780 --> 00:06:04,865
He's a total beginner.

146
00:06:04,906 --> 00:06:06,908
Isn't it a little early
to be on the court?

147
00:06:06,950 --> 00:06:08,535
Yeah, he's got a point.

148
00:06:08,577 --> 00:06:11,413
We don't even know if he has
the stamina for tennis yet.

149
00:06:11,454 --> 00:06:12,998
First we need to see
if you can make it

150
00:06:13,039 --> 00:06:15,208
20 laps around
the school ground,

151
00:06:15,250 --> 00:06:17,210
then we'll show you the courts.

152
00:06:20,922 --> 00:06:24,134
[RINTARO] Hey, how about
everybody does laps?

153
00:06:24,175 --> 00:06:25,844
Let's all welcome
our new teammate!

154
00:06:25,886 --> 00:06:27,262
[GROUP]
Huh?

155
00:06:27,304 --> 00:06:28,096
All of us?

156
00:06:28,138 --> 00:06:31,850
Good idea. Twenty laps,
guys. Let's go!

157
00:06:31,892 --> 00:06:32,893
[whistle blows]

158
00:06:40,400 --> 00:06:42,193
Isn't that the Soft Tennis Club?

159
00:06:42,235 --> 00:06:43,278
That's new.

160
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:45,196
Yeah, looks like the guys' team.

161
00:06:45,238 --> 00:06:47,073
I've never actually
seen them run.

162
00:06:47,115 --> 00:06:49,075
[SOCCER STUDENT 2C]
They must be getting desperate.

163
00:06:52,329 --> 00:06:55,165
It's a waste of time
to start caring now.

164
00:07:05,050 --> 00:07:06,259
[TENNIS STUDENT 2A]
Hey, check this out!

165
00:07:06,301 --> 00:07:07,886
[TENNIS STUDENT 2B]
It's the boys' team.

166
00:07:07,928 --> 00:07:10,138
They're going for
a run? That's nice.

167
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:12,349
Gotta work on that conditioning!

168
00:07:22,484 --> 00:07:24,486
Here's lap three!

169
00:07:24,527 --> 00:07:27,530
Every part of me
feels like it's on fire.

170
00:07:28,615 --> 00:07:32,535
[GROUP panting]

171
00:07:37,624 --> 00:07:40,210
[ITSUKI]
Huh?

172
00:07:40,251 --> 00:07:41,544
Jeez, who is this guy?

173
00:07:41,586 --> 00:07:42,379
Show off!

174
00:07:42,420 --> 00:07:44,005
What sport was he in?

175
00:07:44,047 --> 00:07:45,548
He wasn't.

176
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:47,425
He said he didn't play
anything back at the school

177
00:07:47,467 --> 00:07:49,052
he transferred from.

178
00:08:06,236 --> 00:08:08,613
Huh? Are those guys even human?

179
00:08:08,655 --> 00:08:10,031
‐‐Come on!
‐‐[TSUBASA] Damn it!

180
00:08:10,073 --> 00:08:13,702
Make it stop. I'm dying!

181
00:08:13,743 --> 00:08:16,705
I think I'm gonna be sick.

182
00:08:22,585 --> 00:08:25,046
Pace yourself. Don't
want you to get hurt.

183
00:08:25,088 --> 00:08:26,339
Yeah, well, you're
the one who's not

184
00:08:26,381 --> 00:08:28,508
gonna be able to walk tomorrow.

185
00:08:40,770 --> 00:08:41,730
You're kidding!

186
00:08:41,771 --> 00:08:43,690
Did they really just lap us?

187
00:08:43,732 --> 00:08:45,233
Give it up, Katsuragi.

188
00:08:45,275 --> 00:08:47,318
I'm not gonna stop
till I'm done.

189
00:08:47,360 --> 00:08:50,071
Hey, their running form
actually looks pretty good.

190
00:08:50,113 --> 00:08:52,073
Looks like Shinjo, the captain.

191
00:08:52,115 --> 00:08:54,617
But who's the other
guy? Is he new?

192
00:08:58,663 --> 00:09:00,415
They just keep going.

193
00:09:02,667 --> 00:09:04,919
This is it. The last lap!

194
00:09:19,392 --> 00:09:20,518
[TOMA, MAKI]
Finish!

195
00:09:25,273 --> 00:09:32,030
[TOMA, MAKI panting]

196
00:09:32,072 --> 00:09:37,494
[TOMA] You've never been
in a sports club, seriously?

197
00:09:37,535 --> 00:09:39,204
[MAKI]
Yeah, seriously.

198
00:09:39,245 --> 00:09:41,915
[BOTH panting]

199
00:09:41,956 --> 00:09:44,626
Katsuragi.

200
00:09:44,667 --> 00:09:46,044
Maki.

201
00:09:46,086 --> 00:09:48,505
You've already got
speed and endurance.

202
00:09:48,546 --> 00:09:52,967
You and me can win.
Will you pair up with me?

203
00:09:53,009 --> 00:09:56,429
[MAKI]
Yeah. Shinjo.

204
00:10:00,391 --> 00:10:03,436
[MAKI]
Hey. Toma.

205
00:10:03,478 --> 00:10:06,147
[TOMA]
Huh?

206
00:10:06,189 --> 00:10:08,525
I'm ready, I wanna do this.

207
00:10:08,566 --> 00:10:11,236
Me, too. Thanks, Maki.

208
00:10:18,118 --> 00:10:21,329
[TSUBASA grunting]

209
00:10:21,371 --> 00:10:22,664
Please kill me.

210
00:10:22,705 --> 00:10:25,208
[TSUBASA]
I can't. I'm dead.

211
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:29,921
[GROUP panting]

212
00:10:29,963 --> 00:10:32,632
[TAIYO]
Never again!

213
00:10:32,674 --> 00:10:35,260
[SHINGO]
That was impressive, Katsuragi.

214
00:10:35,301 --> 00:10:37,387
Yeah, you've got real stamina.

215
00:10:37,428 --> 00:10:39,973
See, I'm a power guy,

216
00:10:40,014 --> 00:10:42,517
so I don't care about
speed or endurance.

217
00:10:42,559 --> 00:10:43,893
Nice excuse.

218
00:10:43,935 --> 00:10:46,688
[ITSUKI] I've never run
that much in my whole life.

219
00:10:46,729 --> 00:10:48,439
[TAIYO]
I think I'm gonna puke.

220
00:10:48,481 --> 00:10:50,775
[NAO] I'm pretty sure
I'm all out of puke.

221
00:10:50,817 --> 00:10:53,194
[RINTARO]
Okay, guys. We did it.

222
00:10:53,236 --> 00:10:55,697
Now let's welcome our
newest member to the team.

223
00:10:55,738 --> 00:10:59,325
Come on. Bring it in
for Katsuragi.

224
00:10:59,367 --> 00:11:00,660
‐‐[SHINGO] Welcome aboard.
‐‐[ITSUKI] Yeah.

225
00:11:00,702 --> 00:11:01,661
[NAO]
Good to have you.

226
00:11:01,703 --> 00:11:03,413
‐‐[TSUBASA] Sure.
‐‐[TAIYO] Welcome.

227
00:11:03,454 --> 00:11:04,372
[RINTARO]
Let's go.

228
00:11:04,414 --> 00:11:06,166
[TOMA]
Right.

229
00:11:06,207 --> 00:11:09,669
[ALL groan]

230
00:11:09,711 --> 00:11:11,462
[KANAKO]
What a bunch of morons.

231
00:11:11,504 --> 00:11:12,463
If they wanted to run,

232
00:11:12,505 --> 00:11:13,965
they should have
joined the Track Club.

233
00:11:14,007 --> 00:11:16,467
It's actually scary
how dumb they are.

234
00:11:16,509 --> 00:11:17,635
[YUTA]
Mitsue?

235
00:11:28,021 --> 00:11:30,023
