243
00:11:49,709 --> 00:11:52,670
[STUDENT 1B] I wish, talk about
the worst teacher ever.

244
00:11:52,712 --> 00:11:54,130
Maki, we need to go.

245
00:11:54,172 --> 00:11:57,008
