249
00:12:03,431 --> 00:12:05,975
[TOMA] We're in middle school.
Aren't we both kids?

250
00:12:06,017 --> 00:12:06,809
[MAKI]
You think so?

251
00:12:06,851 --> 00:12:09,270
[STUDENT 1AA] Hey, what are
